        "calc_duration": 0,
        "sort": 0,
        "title": "FAA Headquarters Informed of Flight 11 Hijacking, but Does Not Contact the Pentagon to Request Assistance",
        "source": "History Commons",
        "full_title": "8:32 a.m. September 11, 2001: FAA Headquarters Informed of Flight 11 Hijacking, but Does Not Contact the Pentagon to Request Assistance - History Commons",
