        "title": "Barksdale Air Force Base, Louisiana, Is Participating in an Exercise Based around a Simulated Nuclear Attack",
        "source": "History Commons",
        "full_title": "8:48 a.m. September 11, 2001: Barksdale Air Force Base, Louisiana, Is Participating in an Exercise Based around a Simulated Nuclear Attack - History Commons",
