        "trim": 0,
        "volume": "1.00",
        "mute": false,
        "content": "<p>Personnel and aircraft at Barksdale Air Force Base in Louisiana are participating in the annual US Strategic Command (Stratcom) exercise Global Guardian  .  </p>",
