        "format": "html",
        "jump": 0,
        "trim": 0,
        "volume": "1.00",
        "mute": false,
        "content": "<p>NORAD’s Northeast Air Defense Sector (NEADS) in Rome, NY, has just received a phone call informing it of the hijacking of Flight 175 .  </p>",
