        "content": "<p>The South Tower of the World Trade Center tilts to the southeast and then collapses. It was hit by Flight 175 at 9:03 a.m., 56 minutes earlier .  </p>",
        "image": "http://cdn.historycommons.org/images/events/338_south_tower_collapse2050081722-9613.jpg",
        "image_caption": "The South Tower of the World Trade Center collapses. ",
