        "calc_duration": 0,
        "sort": 0,
        "title": "Fighters Possibly Scrambled from Florida Air Base toward Air Force One, but Apparently Do Not Reach It",
        "source": "History Commons",
        "full_title": "10:00 a.m. September 11, 2001: Fighters Possibly Scrambled from Florida Air Base toward Air Force One, but Apparently Do Not Reach It - History Commons\r",
