        "format": "html",
        "jump": 0,
        "trim": 0,
        "volume": "1.00",
        "mute": false,
        "content": "<p>Fighter jets belonging to a military unit in Jacksonville, Florida, launch to escort Air Force One after it takes off from Sarasota, Florida .  </p>",
        "image": "http://cdn.historycommons.org/images/events/125th_FW_fighter_2050081722-33333.jpg",
