        "calc_duration": 0,
        "sort": 0,
        "title": "United Airlines Publicly Confirms that Flight 175 Has Crashed",
        "source": "History Commons",
        "full_title": "11:53 a.m. September 11, 2001: United Airlines Publicly Confirms that Flight 175 Has Crashed - History Commons",
        "url": "http://historycommons.org/context.jsp?item=a1153uaconfirms#a1153uaconfirms",
        "format": "html",
        "jump": 0,
        "trim": 0,
        "volume": "1.00",
        "mute": false,
        "content": "<p>United Airlines finally issues a press release confirming that Flight 175 has crashed, nearly three hours after this aircraft hit the World Trade Center .  </p>",
